LIMITATIONS and KNOWN ISSUES for release 1.3.0:
* Replicas must only be added/removed for files that are not
  open at any OSD.
* Interrupting the client during read operations does not work.
* Asynchronous writes are not supported.
* Vivaldi is not integrated yet, will be re-integrated in the
  next release.
* init.d files on Fedora require "Defaults requiretty"
  in /etc/sudoers to be removed.
